[16.276508, "o", " hooks already registered in this project?\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(29227 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(6.4s)\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTwo independent questions: (1) which runtime events are hookable → hooks$events, (2) any \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mhooks already registered → hooks$list. No dependencies, so call both in one iteration.\u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mhooks$events\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 3ms, 3.9k chars\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mhooks$list\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 3ms, 11 chars\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(0ms)\u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠹\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mCogitating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (6.4s)\u001b[0m"]
