[40.261902, "o", "                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNote:\u001b[0m Hooks live with the \u001b[1;97mcurrent project\u001b[0m (\u001b[36m.brainyard/hooks/\u001b[0m). Want me to author one? Just tell  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m me the event, the scope (e.g. only when \u001b[36mbash\u001b[0m runs), and the side effect — I'll draft, dry-run,   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m and register it.                                                                                 \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H"]
