[124.881395, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1m\u001b[96mBrainyard TUI\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[36mhook-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[95mclaude-code/opus\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2msession tutorial-21-hooks\u001b[0m \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2mType /help for commands. AI output may be inaccurate.\u001b[0m                     \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ What runtime events can I hook, and are any hooks already registered in this project?\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(29227 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(6.4s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTwo independent questions: (1) w"]
[124.881413, "o", "hich runtime events are hookable → hooks$events, (2) any \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mhooks already registered → hooks$list. No dependencies, so call both in one iteration.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mhooks$events\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 3ms, 3.9k chars\r\n  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mhooks$list\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 3ms, 11 chars\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(32230 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(20.0s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mIteration 1 already fetched both `hooks$events` (full catalog) and `hooks$list` (empty). \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mNo further calls needed. I'll summarize the hookable (`:available? true`) events grouped \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mby category, flag the two gated/unavailable ones, and confirm zero hooks are currently \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mregistered in this project.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[124.881427, "o", "──────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mHookable Runtime Events & Current Hooks\u001b[0m                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mHooks registered in this project:\u001b[0m _None._ The \u001b[36m.brainyard/hooks/\u001b[0m directory has no user-defined    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m hooks yet — \u001b[36mhooks$list\u001b[0m returned empty.                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97m✅ Available events (observer hooks allowed)\u001b[0m                                                     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                            "]
[124.881461, "o", "      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m These are non-gated — your \u001b[36m(fn [event] …)\u001b[0m body receives a sanitized map with the listed payload  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m keys, plus \u001b[36m:event-key\u001b[0m, \u001b[36m:agent-id\u001b[0m, \u001b[36m:defagent-type\u001b[0m.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mGroup\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mEvent\u001b[0m                            \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mPayload keys\u001b[0m                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────┼───────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mAsk\u001b[0m   \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[36magent.ask/pre\u001b[0m                    \u001b[2m │ \u001b"]
